<!-- CSS PARA REMOVER O BOTÃO IMPRIMIR NA VIEW DE IMPRESSÃO E MOSTRAR A IMPRESSÃO SEM O CSS -->
<style type="text/css">
	@media print {
    #printbtn {
        display :  none;
    }
}
#printOnly {
   display : none;
}
@media print {
    #printOnly {
       display : block;
    }
}
</style>

<div id="printbtn">
<%- model_class = Qrpoint -%>
<div class="page-header">
  <h1>QRpoint <%= image_tag (@QRcode) %></h1>
</div>

<dl class="dl-horizontal">
  <dt><strong><%= model_class.human_attribute_name('Descrição') %>:</strong></dt>
  <dd><%= @qrpoint.description %></dd>
  <dt><strong><%= model_class.human_attribute_name('QRcode impresso') %>:</strong></dt>
  <dd><%= @qrpoint.qrcode %></dd>

</dl>

<%= link_to t('.back', :default => t("helpers.links.back")), qrpoints_path, :class => 'btn btn-default' %>
<%= link_to t('.edit', :default => t("helpers.links.edit")), edit_qrpoint_path(@qrpoint), :class => 'btn btn-default' %>
<button type="button" id ="printbtn" class="btn btn-success", onclick ="window.print();return false;">Imprimir</button>
<%= link_to t('.destroy', :default => t("helpers.links.destroy")),
              qrpoint_path(@qrpoint),
              :method => 'delete',
              :data => { :confirm => t('.confirm', :default => t("helpers.links.confirm", :default => 'Are you sure?')) },
              :class => 'btn btn-danger' %>

</div>

<div class="container" id="printOnly" align="center">
<h2>Imprima e recorte o código abaixo inserindo na mesa desejada:</h2>
<br><br><br>
<%= image_tag (@QRcodePrint) %>
</div>
